@model WalkingTec.Mvvm.Core.BaseVM
<style>
    a {
        color: #01aaed
    }
</style>

WTM framework provides a BaseController. All Controller written in the framework should inherit from this base class. BaseController provides many convenient properties and methods

<wt:fieldset field-set-style="Simple" title="Attribute specification">
 </wt:fieldset>
   <table lay-filter="parse-table-demo">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th lay-data="{field:'username', width:200}">Property</th>
                <th lay-data="{field:'joinTime', width:600}">Description</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>ConfigInfo</td>
                <td>Get profile data,For details refers to <a href="/#/Global/Global">global variables</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>GlobaInfo</td>
                <td>Get some global variables.For details refers to<a href="/#/Global/Global"> global variables </a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>UIService</td>
                <td>Get UI service and provide some functions to generate foreground HTML control conveniently</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Cache</td>
                <td>Get cache</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>ParentWindowId</td>
                <td>Get the ID of the parent page of the front-end page</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>CurrentWindowId</td>
                <td>Get the ID of the current window of the front-end page </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>DC</td>
                <td>Database environment</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>LoginUserInfo</td>
                <td>Current login user information</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

<wt:fieldset field-set-style="Simple" title="Method description">
 </wt:fieldset>
   <table lay-filter="parse-table-demo">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th lay-data="{field:'username', width:200}">Method</th>
                <th lay-data="{field:'joinTime', width:600}">Description</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>CreateVM()</td>
                <td>Create a new ViewModel. All VMS in the framework should be created in the Controller through this function</td>
